data.meta_site_name: Our Friendly World with Fawn and Matt
data.text:
This is a podcast on the Art of Friendship (how to make and keep lasting friendships).

Welcome to "Our Friendly World with Fawn and Matt," the podcast that takes you on a heartwarming journey through diverse cultures, inspiring stories, and fascinating conversations. Join your hosts, Fawn and Matt, as they explore the beauty of our global community, spreading positivity, empathy, and understanding. Immerse yourself in engaging discussions with guests from around the world, sharing their unique experiences and perspectives. Tune in for uplifting tales, enlightening insights, and a warm embrace of the human spirit. Discover the magic that connects us all in this delightful podcast where friendship knows no boundaries.
